	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=61546><span id=Sage>Slipskin</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>1090 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.65]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Follow up - Bard mana regen song will regen mana for everyone in the party - except for the bard playing the song&nbsp;&nbsp;:(  Bard's cannot regen their own mana.  Its sick but from what I have read its true.<br><br>Bard songs are classified as spells in most cases, I believe.  Check out EQDiva.com to find more info on what stacks and what doesn't.<br><br>Bards are the 3rd best soloing class in the game after Necros and Druids.  I have yet to get it right but I have heard that it is possible to quad kite with a bard.  I know you can fear kite with one at level 26.</p>&nbsp;<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222</a><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760</a></td></td></tr>
